{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Multi Payment","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"FluxStore - Universal mobile commerce Flutter app for Magento, WooCommerce and Opencart","meta_description":"Fluxstore is universal app that fully integration with the Woocommerce, Mangeto and Opencart","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"fluxstore","toc":null,"keywords":["fluxstore","flutter app","fluxstore","Magento app","Woo Commerce app","Opencart app"]},"html":"<h3 id=\"webview-multi-payment\"><a href=\"#webview-multi-payment\" aria-label=\"webview multi payment permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Webview Multi-Payment</h3>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/3b3c6/payment.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 93.3977455716586%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"payment\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/efcfb/payment.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/11053/payment.png 200w,\n/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/1b42c/payment.png 400w,\n/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/efcfb/payment.png 800w,\n/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/d25cb/payment.png 1200w,\n/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/3b3c6/payment.png 1242w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>The current release on support for multi payment for WooCommerce website, once you config it run success on the website, it can be run smoothly from the app, add new payment key value and the image URL to enable it:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Payments <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"paypal\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"assets/icons/payment/paypal.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"stripe\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"assets/icons/payment/stripe.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"razorpay\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"assets/icons/payment/razorpay.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"404-error-page\"><a href=\"#404-error-page\" aria-label=\"404 error page permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>404 error page</h3>\n<p>One enable the mstore-api plugin the payment gateway may could not work as default, to fix the error when click Process payment, following these step:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Update the Mstore API to latest version: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mstore-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wordpress.org/plugins/mstore-api/</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Copy the file \"plugins/mstore-api/templates/mstore-api-template.php\" to your current Wordpress template folder (example: wp-content/themes/your-template-name)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Go back to Wordpress Admin dasboard and create a page and name it \"mstore-api\" and remember don't set any parent page for it, then set page template to \"Mstore Checkout\"</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"native-payment-for-razopay-paypal-tap\"><a href=\"#native-payment-for-razopay-paypal-tap\" aria-label=\"native payment for razopay paypal tap permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Native payment for Razopay, Paypal, Tap</h3>\n<p>Current release support to work with new Native Payment Paypal, Razopay and Tap, this gateway is compatible for all WooCommerce, Magento and Opencart.</p>\n<p>Please review this video for more detail on how to config the payments:</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MrDq3CqRphY\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>","fields":{"slug":"/fluxstore/multi-payment/"},"timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Webview Multi-Payment The current release on support for multi payment for WooCommerce website, once you config it run success on theâ€¦","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/projects/inspireui-documents/docs/content/fluxstore/multi-payment.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/fluxstore/multi-payment/"}}